manual
step 1) connect ssh
step 2) use whoami command to check the user
cmd: whoami
step 3) to check hostname
cmd: hostname
step 4) to check os info
cmd: uname -a
step 5) to find correct version of linux
cmd: cat /etc/issue
step 6) also use 
cmd: cat /proc/version
step 7) check the permission 
cmd: id
Step 8) check the processer
cmd: ps -A
or
cmd: ps aux
Step 9) using evn
cmd: evn
Step 10) to check the user path
cmd: cat /etc/passwd
Step 10) find hash file
cmd: sudo cat /etc/shadow

Networking
step 1)to check connect devices
cmd: netstat -a

